ilakukan dibuat sebisa mungkin mematuhi printip pronsip syariah</p><p>Mulai dari akad, lalu serah terima barang sampai keterlambatan pembayaran cicilan.</p><p>Waktu itu usaha kami mengalami penurunan omset yg cukup signifikan sehingga beberapa bulan usaha kami ga bisa utk membayar cicilan</p><p>Alhmdulillahnya Pokdal JOS (Amanah Foundation) memberi pemqkluman dan memudahkan kami dengan memberi tenggat waktu</p><p>Alhmdulillah setelah usaha kami membaik hutang hapenya langsung kami lunasin semuanya</p><p>Sukses buat Pokdal JOS (Amanah Foundation) semoga tambah berkah dan lebih memberi banyak manfaat utk umat </p>"},"image":{"type":"image","label":"Gambar","value":"https://ukm.digital/builder_uploads/2020/03/builder_20200317134857466566613.JPG"},"lightbox":{"type":"text","label":"Lightbox Video URL","value":""},"reverse":{"type":"switch","label":"Tukar Layout","horizontal":true,"value":true}},"style":{"fullwidth":{"type":"switch","horizontal":true,"label":"Lebar Konten Penuh","value":false},"padding":{"type":"directional","label":"Jarak Konten","value":{"top":100,"bottom":100,"left":0,"right":0}},"content_color":{"type":"select","horizontal":true,"label":"Warna Konten","value":"default","options":{"light":"Light","dark":"Dark","default":"Default"}},"background":{"type":"background","value":{"backgroundColor":"#FFFFFF","backgroundImage":"","backgroundPosition":"center","backgroundSize":"cover","backgroundRepeat":"no-repeat","backgroundAttachment":"scroll"}},"overlay_color":{"type":"overlay","horizontal":true,"label":"Background Overlay","value":"rgba(0,0,0,0)"},"divider":{"type":"divider","label":"Pembatas antar block","value":{"top":{"type":"none","color":"white","width":100,"height":100,"invert":false},"bottom":{"type":"none","color":"white","width":100,"height":100,"invert":false}}}},"id":"7f1faf10-681b-11ea-9eb2-7ba96fb895da","name":"Content 5"}},{"id":"94","name":"Quote Nabi Muhammad","blocks":{"blockID":"content-03","title":"Content 3","screenshot":"https://ukm.d